# GitHub MCP Integration Guidelines

## MCP Server Usage
- Leverage GitHub MCP server capabilities for repository operations
- Use GitHub API instead of direct git commands when possible
- Implement proper authentication and error handling for GitHub operations
- Follow GitHub API rate limiting best practices

## Repository Management
- Use MCP tools for repository creation, cloning, and modification
- Implement proper GitHub workflow integration
- Handle GitHub webhooks and API responses appropriately
- Maintain consistent repository structure and documentation

## Best Practices
- Always validate GitHub operations before execution
- Implement proper error recovery for API failures
- Use GitHub's REST and GraphQL APIs efficiently
- Follow GitHub's security and access control guidelines